node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Mothership.sg in Singapore. Image may contain: one or more people, text that says '528 new Covid-19 cases in S'pore, over 16,000 cases in total More More details details will be provided tonight. HAS'

node.text:
JUST IN: Six of the new cases today are Singaporeans or Permanent Residents. 
The vast majority of the cases are Work Permit holders residing in foreign worker dormitories.

Total number of confirmed cases in Singapore so far: 16,169.
